LanguageData.Ratkin.label: Ratkin
LanguageData.Ratkin.description: It is a human like a rodent gene. Although the origin is unknown, it is a monarchy society based on agricultural society. There are more female objects than males, and it is difficult to distinguish the gender of the object when viewed from the outside.
